Output docs/assets/eval_demo.gif
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1400
Set Height 900
Set Padding 30
Set Theme "Catppuccin Macchiato"
Set WindowBar Colorful

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Type "./bin/swarm"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "/eval"
Sleep 1s
Type " list"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "/eval scenario_1"
Enter
Sleep 45s

Type "/exit"
Enter
Sleep 1s
